Cyberpunk-style illustration: Two figures stand on separate floating platforms in a neon-lit digital void, facing each other across a chasm of swirling data streams and glowing circuit patterns. One figure is clad in sleek corporate attire with holographic financial charts orbiting their head like a halo. The other wears a tech-heavy jacket covered in cables and ports, surrounded by floating geometric code symbols and server rack silhouettes. Between them, a fragile bridge made of translucent currency symbols and binary code is half-constructed, glowing warm amber where the pieces connect. The atmosphere is moody with deep purple and electric blue lighting, rain falling through holographic advertisements. Both figures extend hands toward the unfinished bridge, their fingertips almost touching where the two visual languages merge into a unified golden light.
